articles.author: Sonnet Swire and Evan Perez, CNN
articles.title: Kansas woman led female ISIS battalion in Syria, prosecutors say - CNN
articles.description: An American woman from Kansas who allegedly joined ISIS and led an all-woman battalion in Syria has been arrested and charged by federal prosecutors with providing and conspiring to provide material support to a foreign terrorist organization.
